020/11/lashana-lynch-bond-backlash-black-woman-007-1234597026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2020%2F11%2Flashana-lynch-bond-backlash-black-woman-007-1234597026%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8pKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=29897ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/lashana-lynch-bond-backlash-black-woman-007-1234597026/</a><br />\n根本就冇confirmed 會係下一任007主角囉<br />\n佢係James Bond 上集退左休先接手007呢個代號咁姐，講到佢做主角咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769eec3bc3c06bed32a7d088da03e144a8ec070d","tid":2273853,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"唔會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c885c97c08cda6e44ef4a1e002d634c3a8bbf4e2","tid":2273853,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704aa00a7c4b9ff4806810e5f3f1bd9a34010ad1","tid":2273853,"uid":190789,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"你做主角，唔叫James Bond，邊個care<br />\n你叫Lebron James都得。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"叫RmbJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}